data.description: Sun filled, two story townhome in Bristol Bay Subdivision featuring an open concept floor plan and freshly painted throughout! Spacious living /dining room with new laminate flooring. Great kitchen with breakfast bar, 42" cabinets and pleny of countertop space. Quaint patio for that morning cup of coffee. Second floor has a fantastic loft, great for an entertainment or gaming area, or can easily be converted in a third bedroom. Primary bedroom has a walk in closet and shared full bath. Convenient second floor laundry and attached two car garage. Extra amenities include a year round clubhouse, exercise facilities, playground, walking/biking trails and two pools. Please note that there is a not a homeowners tax exemption on the home.
